snippet.title: Paper Mario (N64) - All bosses in the same battle (Release & Download)
snippet.description:
Link:
https://www.mediafire.com/folder/jx73upbyffksi/Release

I really recommend using fast forward and not trying this on console lol

Remember to set the RAM to 8MB and disable register caching (only for PJ64).

Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/eldexter
